column5: Congratulations to Ann Rocchi who is the winner of the 2 passes to Bass Talk 2007! Thank you to all who entered our contest! For the unfortunate non-winners you can still register, for full info please visit our web-site at www.basstalk.ca The first sessions are less than 2 weeks away!  Regards, Dave
You spelt my name wrong David. LOL   Congrats Ann
